How to install
--------------

pedalog-tool requires libpedalog and its headers to be installed.
It also requires cmake to be installed.

To install:

1) Go into pedalog-tool directory
2) cmake .

As root:
3) make install

This has been tested on Linux and Windows (using MinGW).

Any problems please report on GitHub: https://github.com/greenlynx/pedalog-tool/issues
